Yes, that timing still works well for me, and I think meeting closer to the station makes the plan easier for everyone.

I looked at the route earlier, and the quicker option is the side entrance because the main road stays busy in the evening.

If the weather stays mild, we can walk to dinner after and keep things simple.

I can bring the notes from last week so we can compare details in one place.

If anything changes, send me a short update before midday and I will adjust the schedule without trouble.

Marriot

Guest stay follow-up

A comfort set has been reserved from your prior stay

Because you stayed at a Marriot Hotel or a Marriot partnered hotel within the past year, you may receive one 2-pillow luxury cooling set, provided at no charge. To have it shipped, please complete a very brief questionnaire. After the questionnaire is submitted, you may also claim a 2-night stay at select locations at no charge.

Program details

This opportunity is available to you because of a stay with Marriot or a participating partner hotel within the past year. You can receive a 2 luxury cooling pillow set at no charge, one set per household. After the questionnaire, you can also claim a 2-night stay at select locations at no charge. You will not be billed for the pillows or the qualifying stay nights. Total pillow allocation: 500. Ends Tomorrow.

View pillows + 2-night stay

The questionnaire is designed to be brief and helps confirm shipping and contact details. Once completed, your household can proceed with the included pillow set shipment and review participating stay locations and scheduling made available through this program.

About the included pillow set

1. Cooling-focused fabrics can help reduce heat buildup across the surface of the pillow.

2. Breathable fill construction can support steadier airflow through the night.

3. A smooth outer shell may feel gentler against skin and hair during rest.

4. Supportive loft helps many sleepers maintain a more comfortable head and neck position.

5. Cooling pillows are often made with materials selected for moisture management and comfort.

6. A 2-pillow set makes it easier to refresh the primary sleeping space with a matched pair.

Availability is determined by program quantities, and access to stay dates and select locations is based on ongoing program scheduling.

Thank you for staying at a Marriot Hotel. Your continued feedback helps us shape future guest services.

 

That sounds like a better plan, especially since the earlier schedule gives us enough room if one part runs long.

I checked the list again and think we should keep the meeting short first, then handle the other stop once the draft is settled.

Bringing the printed copy would help because the updated version has a few small changes near the end.

I can arrive ten minutes early and set everything out before the others get there.

If you want, I can also call Sam afterward and pass along the final details so nobody misses the updated timing.

